{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"c4864be7-35f6-45a0-9123-dce094dd1d74","content":"No repo-specific guidance here, so here's the general migration path:\n\n## Migrating from VSTest@3 to Microsoft.Testing.Platform\n\n### 1. Update your test projects\n\nAdd the MSTest runner and enable the new platform:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n  <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### 2. Replace the pipeline task\n\nReplace `VSTest@3` with `DotNetCoreCLI@2` (or a plain `dotnet test` script):\n\n```yaml\n# Before\n- task: VSTest@3\n  inputs:\n    testAssemblies: '**/*Tests.dll'\n    codeCoverageEnabled: true\n\n# After\n- task: DotNetCoreCLI@2\n  displayName: 'Run Tests'\n  inputs:\n    command: test\n    projects: '**/*Tests.csproj'\n    arguments: >-\n      --logger \"trx;LogFileName=results.trx\"\n      --results-directory $(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults\n      --collect \"Code Coverage\"\n```\n\n### 3. Publish results & coverage\n\n```yaml\n- task: PublishTestResults@2\n  inputs:\n    testResultsFormat: VSTest\n    testResultsFiles: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.trx'\n\n- task: PublishCodeCoverageResults@2\n  inputs:\n    summaryFileLocation: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.cobertura.xml'\n```\n\n### Key notes\n\n- **TRX**: The `--logger trx` argument produces the same `.trx` files `VSTest@3` generated.\n- **Code coverage**: `--collect \"Code Coverage\"` uses the built-in collector. For Cobertura format (needed by `PublishCodeCoverageResults@2`), add the `coverlet.collector` NuGet package and use `--collect \"XPlat Code Coverage\"` instead.\n- **`TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport`** ensures `dotnet test` delegates to the new Microsoft.Testing.Platform host rather than the legacy VSTest engine.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"d92471e7-4ca0-4e66-892a-8da7bf87b33a","outputTokens":541,"requestId":"E84D:342B39:26DE9D6:2954B56:6A0493B1"},"id":"50e0111c-6228-4bcc-98bd-b8f55ebf40d9","timestamp":"2026-05-13T15:07:42.115Z","parentId":"bd605bb2-42cf-4789-8c5c-8deca1673d01"}
